  "text": "Genomic analysis was conducted on chromosomes 1 to 19, X and Y of mouse build mm9. Mouse ENCODE data [CITATION_1] comprising open chromatin DNaseI data that was collected at embryonic day 11.5 in the mesoderm and histone (H3K4me1, H3K4me3, and H3K27ac) data collected from embryonic day 14.5 for heart and liver were downloaded from the UCSC genome repository (goldenPath).",
